Volkswagen Buys Karmann Remainder Today, Handelsblatt Reports

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-02-28T06:28:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/volkswagen-buys-karmann-remainder-today-handelsblatt-reports.html
  Volkswagen AG  will buy carmaker
Wilhelm Karmann GmbH’s metal unit today from insolvency
administrator Ottmar Hermann, saving 320 jobs,  Handelsblatt 
reported, citing Hermann. The rights for the name Karmann
haven’t been sold yet, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 